OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally cloudy day with
OL,6,Fsome showery rain, some heavy and
OL,7,Fmerging into some longer spells of
OL,8,Frain especially over Ross and Cromarty
OL,9,Fand Sutherland. The Isles likely
OL,10,Fhaving the best of the drier weather.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome persistent rain over
OL,13,FNorth Highland this evening turning
OL,14,Fshowery from the south. A few clear
OL,15,Fintervals overnight but still rather
OL,16,Fcloudy with a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
