OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FQuite cloudy but some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny intervals developing,
OL,7,Falong with a few showers which could
OL,8,Fturn heavy and thundery in the far
OL,9,Fnorth. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,13,Fmix of bright spells and showers,
OL,14,Fthese heavy and thundery over East
OL,15,FHighland on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
